{
  "texts": [
    "These cell crops are used in all the deep learning workflows.",
    "CellProfiler 60 allows the construction of customizable automated pipelines for analysis of biological images.",
    "It facilitates the analysis and extraction of meaningful information from high-throughput imaging experiments.",
    "The pipeline starts with image import, then it is followed by image pre-processing, such as illumination correction and noise removal.",
    "Then the objects are identified: nuclei are identified first and with this prior information the boundaries of the whole cell are inferred."
  ]
}